DiffuPercom: A novel simplex-based diffusion framework for personalized
comment generation

Associated article authors: Jiamiao Liu, Pengsen Cheng, Jinqiao Dai, and
Jiayong Liu.

This distribution contains code adapted from the Simplex Diffusion Language
Model project, identified by the original package metadata as:
https://github.com/allenai/diffusion

The file sdlm/models/roberta/modeling_roberta_modified.py is adapted from
Hugging Face Transformers 4.27.1. Its original copyright and Apache License 2.0
header is retained.

Third-party Python packages are dependencies and are not redistributed in this
source archive. Third-party baseline repositories from the research workspace
are also not included.
